    • findFood

      public ArrayList<Meal> findFood(double proteins, double carbs, double kcals, double fat, String category)
      Returns a list of meals that match the given nutritional requirements and food category.
      Parameters:
      proteins - the amount of proteins in grams desired for each meal
      carbs - the amount of carbohydrates in grams desired for each meal
      kcals - the number of calories desired for each meal
      fat - the amount of fat in grams desired for each meal
      category - the food category desired, or "normal" for any category
      Returns:
      a list of Meal objects that match the nutritional requirements and food category
